msg: TCP Lateral now uses a queuing zombie service during recovery. | Refactored UDP Discovery. | Slots for same key updates now get added to the disk recycle bin. | Added File Disk	Cache. | Default properties should now work. | Caught Throwable in JDBC disk cache shrinker, so it won't die.
